"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-culture-culture-news-olympic-boxing-champion-imane-khelif-files-online-harassment-complaint-paris-1235078078\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"BySimon Vozick-Levinson Three days ago, Algerian boxer Imane Khelifwon a gold medalin the women's welterweight division of the 2024Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"BySimon Vozick-Levinson\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 23}, {\"ngram\": \"Algerian boxer Imane Khelifwon\", \"from\": 40, \"to\": 70}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medalin\", \"from\": 71, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's welterweight division\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It should have been a triumphant moment for an athlete who spent years training for this moment and won all four of her matches on the world's biggest stage.\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a triumphant moment\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 181}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 196}, {\"ngram\": \"years training\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"her matches\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest stage\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, her victory was shadowed by a relentless campaign ofbad-faith criticismfocused on factually baseless claims about hergender.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her victory\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 320}, {\"ngram\": \"a relentless campaign ofbad-faith\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"factually baseless claims\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"hergender\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because the games took place in France, which hasrobust lawsagainst online hate speech, Khelif has now filed a legal complaint with a Paris prosecutor's office.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9924227544267463, \"rank\": 0.006825958004653309, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.4585936422545265e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"lawsagainst online hate speech\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"a legal complaint\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to theAssociated Press, Khelif's lawyers filed the complaint alleging \\\"aggravated cyber-harassment\\\" on Aug. 9, the day she won the gold medal.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theAssociated Press\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif's lawyers\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"the complaint\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"aggravated cyber-harassment\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The complaint reportedly does not name a specific perpetrator; instead, the prosecutor's office will conduct an investigation and decide whether to charge anyone under the statute, which could call for two to five years in prison and tens of thousands of Euros in fines.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The complaint\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific perpetrator\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"the prosecutor's office\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 844}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"the statute\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"two to five years\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"tens of thousands\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"Euros\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"fines\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attorney Nabil Boudi wrotein the complaintthat the campaign of \\\"speculation fueled by malicious individuals\\u2026 exceeded 100 million views\\\" on the X platform, becoming an \\\"ordeal\\\" for Khelif.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Attorney Nabil Boudi\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaign\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"speculation\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"malicious individuals\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"100 million views\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"the X platform\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"ordeal\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I send a message to all the people of the world to uphold the Olympic principles and the Olympic Charter, to refrain from bullying all athletes, because this has effects, massive effects,\\\" Khelif reportedly told the sports video news service SNTV.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"all the people\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic principles\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Charter\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"all athletes\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"effects\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"massive effects\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports video news service SNTV\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added that online harassment \\\"can destroy people, it can kill people's thoughts, spirit and mind.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"online harassment\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1513}, {\"ngram\": \"people's thoughts\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"spirit\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can divide people.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And because of that, I ask them to refrain from bullying.\\\"\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The manufactured right-wing controversy around Khelif began on Aug. 1, when her opponent, Italian boxer Angela Carini, withdrew from a bout after just 46 seconds, saying, \\\"I have never been hit so hard in my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1735, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9918651035986105, \"rank\": 0.005916156043566746, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1749, \"end\": 1762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \